Athletic Physicals for Winter Athletes Grades 7-12 – Deadline 11/14



If Winter season is the first sport your son/daughter has played this school year – Complete the Winter First Time Registrants on FamilyID and return or upload Sections 5 & 6.



If your son/daughter has already played a Fall sport and will now be playing a Winter sport – Complete the Winter Recertification on FamilyID and return or upload Section 7. (Section 8 is only necessary if there has been an injury)



Additional information and directions can be found at https://www.freeport.k12.pa.us/Content2/384. Questions can be directed to abbott@freeport.k12.pa.us
